				{
					"type": "thinking_start"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "The user wants me to think about and then write a 300-word essay on agentic AI context management. This is a writing/",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "thinking task, not a coding task. Let me think carefully about the topic and",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " craft a well-written essay.\n\nLet me consider the key aspects of agentic AI context management:\n\n1. What is context",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " in agentic AI? - The working memory that AI agents",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " operate with, including conversation history, tool results, system instructions, and retrieved information.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "\n\n2. Why is it challenging? - Context windows are finite, information accum",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "ulates rapidly during multi-step tasks, and agents must decide what to retain, summar",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "ize, or discard.\n",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "\n\n3",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": ". Key strategies - Hierarchical summarization, selective retrieval, structured memory systems, tool-based exploration vs. in-context retention.\n\n4. The fundamental tension - Between having enough context to make good decisions and not overwhelming the window with irrelevant detail.\n\n5. Real-world implications",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " - Affects task completion rates, coherence over long sessions, cost efficiency.\n\nNow I'm thinking about how to structure the essay itself",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": ". I should open with the core problem—that agents",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " need to juggle limited context while handling increasingly complex tasks—then explore the tension between retention and efficiency, discuss",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " practical strategies like summarization and selective memory, and close with why this matters for building",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " reliable AI systems. I'll aim for clear, direct language that avoids jargon while maintaining intellectual",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " rigor.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_stop"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "Let me think through the structure and argument before writing",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ".\n\nThe core tension worth exploring: context management is fundamentally a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " *compression* problem -- agents must decide what matters before they can decide",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " what to do. The essay should avoid generic AI hype",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " and instead examine the actual mechanics and tradeoffs.\n\nStructure",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ": problem framing, the fundamental tension, emerging strategies",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ", a forward-looking insight.\n\n---\n\n## The Bottleneck That Thinks",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "\n\nEvery agentic AI system runs into the same wall: the context window is finite, but the world",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " is not. An agent tasked with modifying a large codebase, resear",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "ching a complex topic, or orchestrating multi-step workflows must continuously decide what information to hold close and what to let",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " go. This is context management -- and it is arguably the defining challenge of agentic AI today",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ".\n\nThe problem is harder than it appears. A naive approach fills the context",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " window greedily: every file read, every tool result, every intermediate",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " reasoning step accumulates until the agent is swimming in tokens,",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " most of them irrelevant to the current decision. Performance degrades not from",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " lack of information but from excess of it. The signal drowns in noise the agent",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " itself created.\n\nEffective context management requires the agent to act as its own editor",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ". Hierarchical summarization compresses earlier work into distilled representations. Selective retrieval -- searching",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " files on demand rather than pre-loading them -- trades lat",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "ency for headroom. Structured delegation splits work across sub-agents, each with a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " focused context tailored to a narrow subtask. The best systems",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " combine all three, treating context not as a log but",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " as a curated workspace.\n\nWhat makes this genuinely difficult is that relevance is task-dependent and",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " shifts mid-execution. Information discarded in step three may",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " become critical in step twelve. Every summarization is a bet",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " that the compressed representation preserves what will matter later. Get it",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " wrong and the agent loses coherence, repeats work, or sil",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "ently drops constraints.\n\nThe deeper insight is this: context management is not a peripheral engineering concern",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ". It is the agent's epistemology -- the mechanism by which it decides what it",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " knows. Improving it does not merely make agents faster or cheaper",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ". It makes them meaningfully more capable of sustained, coherent reasoning over the",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " kind of complex tasks that justify building agents in the first place.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a62943001E2bH7O1p1hwxBn"
				},
				{
